        <inbodydescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Performs input parameters validation. Return error code if input parameters are invalid</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para><para>Fill IPI Payload</para><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Send an IPI request to the PLM by using the XPlmi_InPlacePlmUpdate CDO command Wait for IPI response from PLM with a timeout.</para></listitem><listitem><para>If the timeout exceeds then error is returned otherwise it returns the status of the IPI response.</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>        </inbodydescription>
